{"tid":736223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府總部外垃圾桶遭縱火　重案組接手調查","createTime":"2018-07-10T05:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T05:43:00.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d30a1480998867f8a6afd913fc6b148b34249b3","tid":736223,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180710/photo/bkn-20180710121415238-0710_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180710133417\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180710%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180710121415238-0710_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180710133417&h=cd561ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府總部對開發生縱火案。今日(10日)早上11時37分，添美道2號政府總部對開，通往海富中心的扶手電梯旁垃圾桶起火，途人發現報警。警員趕至拉喉將火救熄，垃圾桶嚴重焚毀，消防在場調查發現桶內留有易燃液體，認為起火原因有可疑，警方列作縱火案，由中區重案組接手調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180710/bkn-20180710121415238-0710_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180710%2Fbkn-20180710121415238-0710_00822_001.html&d=G3HZ6pmG21M7rxM7%2BVX0BaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=77389492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180710/bkn-20180710121415238-0710_00822_001.html</a>"}]}